title: 2BR 1BA apt, Modern kitchen, Open concept plan, Generous storage
posting_body: ['Our Bellevue apartments and town homes – adjacent to Goldsmith Park and directly across the street from the Microsoft campus – are surrounded by lush landscaping and soaring trees, feeling as if you are in the secluded country.', 'But with businesses, great shopping and dining close by in downtown Redmond and at Redmond Town Center, you never feel far from anything.', 'Each apartment home provides spacious floor plans, modern kitchens, designer touches, and plenty of storage.', 'Enjoy fabulous amenities as well, including outdoor pools, fitness centers and business lounge.', 'This apartment features:', 'Open concept living, dining and kitchen', 'Fully-equipped kitchen w/ microwave', 'Large windows throughout', 'Generous storage', 'Private patio', 'Convenient washer and dryer inside', 'Wood Burning Fireplace', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'Come Visit us!', 'Redmond Park Apartments', '14700 NE 35th', 'St', 'Bellevue, WA 98007', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours: Monday - Saturday 9:00 am - 6:00 pm', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'related search terms :::: bellevue, downtown redmond, redmond park, redmond town center, over lake mall, crossroads mall, bellevue square, goldsmith park, lake sammamish, lake washington, marymoor park, bellevue municipal golf course, burke-gillman trail, bellevue college, digipen institute of technology, lake washington technical college, bellevue school district, highway 520, microsoft shuttle, microsoft campus']
